Summary: i was looking at the stars and seen a moving object go in between the 2 stars.then disappear.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was working at the airport and its about. 7:30am. I was fueling a plane and looking at these 2 stars and I catch a light heading between the stars. As the light gets closer to the stars,the 1 on the bottom started blinking,the 1 on the top starts blinking as the light goespast the stars. And the light disappeared. I had an Erie filling. The light had no tracer, so it wasn't a shooting star.
